data-ad-slot="2887095024"></ins> <script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script> </div><p><strong>11</strong>. Create an xml file named <strong>activity_login.xml</strong> under <strong>res â layout</strong>.</p><pre class="brush: xml; title: activity_login.xml; notranslate" title="activity_login.xml">
